<HL>
   Politics &amp; Policy:
   Senate Democrats Ready Legislation
   To Overhaul the Health-Care System
   ----
   By Hilary Stout
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
05/28/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A24
</SO>
<CO>
   LABOR TAXES
</CO>
